  "title": "Claude 杀疯了？三年爆赚 700 亿＋现金流 170 亿",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652648462&idx=3&sn=25370a9b11a5341586b0cfde106bade9",
  "date": "2025-11-24 05:22:00",
